Lemma nth_error_in_bounds: forall {A} (l: list A) i, (O <= i < length l)%nat -> exists x, nth_error l i = value x.
induction i; destruct l; intros; simpl in *; try solve [eauto|omegaContradiction].
Lemma nth_eq_nth_error_eq: forall {A} (d: A) (l l': list A) i, (O <= i < length l)%nat -> length l = length l' -> nth i l d = nth i l' d -> nth_error l i = nth_error l' i.
intros until i; intros H H0 H1.
revert i l l' H H0 H1.
induction i; destruct l; destruct l'; intros; simpl in *; try solve [auto|omegaContradiction].
Lemma core_load_fun: forall ch m loc v1 v2, core_load ch loc v1 m -> core_load ch loc v2 m -> v1=v2.
